<title>USA: Century Comms adds to share buyback.</title>
<headline>Century Comms adds to share buyback.</headline>
<dateline>NEW CANAAN, Conn. 1997-08-13</dateline>
<text>
<p>Century Communications Corp said Wendesday that its board of directors authorized the repurchase of up to an additional five million shares of common stock.</p>
<p>Century's previously authorized purchase was up to two million shares, of which 907,500 were purchased through August 12, 1997.</p>
<p>This authorization brings the total available for repurchase to 6,092,000 shares.</p>
